	<p>There are 3 ways to Install Node.js：</br>1,by the Installation package</br>2,by compiling the source code</br>3,by yum|apt-get in Linux Environment and by <a href="http://brew.sh/" target="_blank">Homebrew</a> in Mac</br>For Windows and Mac users，we advise to install by the Installation package，and Linux users by compiling the source code。</p>

	<h4><a id="user-content-windows-和-mac-Install" class="anchor" href="#windows-和-mac-Install" aria-hidden="true"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Windows 和 Mac Install：</h4>

	<p><strong>Step 1:</strong></p>

	<p>Open the <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank">Node.js website</a>, you can see the two options below:</p>

	<p><a href="/img/book/1.1.1.png" target="_blank"><img src="/img/book/1.1.1.png" alt="" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>

	<p>The left one is for LTS version，if you know ubuntu you will be familiar with it, that is Long-Term Support version，it's enough for most people。The right one is the latest version，support the latest language features（like a more comprehensive support for ES6），if you want to try some new features, you can choose this.This time we choose the left v6.9.1 LTS to download。</p>

	<blockquote>
	<p>Tips:From <a href="http://node.green">http://node.green</a> we can see how do all versions of Node.js support ES6.</p>
	</blockquote>

	<p><strong>Step 2:</strong></p>

	<p>Install Node.js，just click the next botton.</p>

	<p><a href="/img/book/1.1.2.png" target="_blank"><img src="/img/book/1.1.2.png" alt="" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>

